
        MOVIE DATABASE APPLICATION

 '/'

    Top 20 movies scorted by average vote score. At least 50 votes required to be taken into account.

 '/topGenre'

    Displays a pie chart presenting a percentage of various genre representation in the movie database.

 '/search'

    Allows for a search through the movie database. You may choose up to two parameters:
    1. Movie genre, 2. Minimum average vote value.

 '/movie/:id'

    This page displays specific data regarding a chosen movie:
    - title
    - average vote score
    - genres that the film is representing
    - description of the movie, downloaded through OMDB API (http://www.omdbapi.com)

Technologies used:
    Java 8 (1.8.0.40)
    Play Framework 2.4.1